ion_id": 7, "key_findings": "6 active MCP servers with 5 infrastructure duplication categories (API clients, embeddings, vector DBs, databases, coordination). 3-tier strategy: shared core library (dopemux-core), infrastructure consolidation, maintain MCP independence. -60% code duplication, -16% containers, 17-day roadmap."}, {"name": "Data Flow & Call Patterns", "decision_id": 8, "key_findings": "7 anti-patterns identified: Phantom Orchestrator (Integration Bridge read-only vs documented orchestrator), Isolated Islands (zero MCP-to-MCP), Unknown Decision Flow, Redis Ghost Bus, Synchronous API Gauntlet (4 MCPs duplicate calls), ConPort Split-Brain, No Circuit Breakers. Service mesh strategy: -75% API costs, -60% latency, +200% throughput. Extends Decision #7 to 21 days (+4)."}], "remaining_tasks": ["Deep dive: MCP Server Consolidation (infrastructure duplication, separation strategy)", "Deep dive: Data Flow & Call Patterns (anti-patterns, optimization opportunities)", "Synthesize findings and update ARCHITECTURE-CONSOLIDATION-SYNTHESIS.md"], "files_analyzed": ["docker-compose.unified.yml", "services/serena/v2/intelligence/database.py", "services/conport/src/context_portal_mcp/core/embedding_service.py", "services/dope-context/src/search/hybrid_search.py", "services/serena/v2/adhd_features.py", "services/adhd_engine/engine.py", "services/conport_kg/adhd_query_adapter.py"], "methodology": "Zen thinkdeep 5-step systematic analysis: (1) Plan, (2) Evidence gathering, (3) Architecture design, (4) Validation, (5) Summary. Confidence levels: high\u2192very_high\u2192almost_certain.", "files_updated": ["/Users/hue/code/dopemux-mvp/docs/ARCHITECTURE-CONSOLIDATION-SYNTHESIS.md"], "ready_for_implementation": true, "key_decisions": ["Replace MetaMCP broker with profile-based MCP selection", "70% context reduction (50+ tools to 10-15 per profile)", "3-phase rollout: backward compatible, opt-in profiles, smart auto-detect", "ADHD Engine integration for energy-aware profile suggestions"]}, "change_source": "update_active_context"}
