, profiles/minimal.yaml, docs/UI-DESIGN-RESEARCH-SYNTHESIS.md (comprehensive reference), docs/PROFILE-YAML-SCHEMA.md (already exists). ALL TESTS PASSING: 4/4 profiles load successfully, detection engine scores correctly, config generator validates all MCPs. NEXT SESSION: Task 1.4 CLI Commands (1 hour to complete Epic 1 MVP).", "git_files_to_commit": ["src/dopemux/profile_models.py", "src/dopemux/profile_parser.py", "src/dopemux/profile_detector.py", "src/dopemux/config_generator.py", "profiles/developer.yaml", "profiles/researcher.yaml", "profiles/architect.yaml", "profiles/minimal.yaml", "docs/UI-DESIGN-RESEARCH-SYNTHESIS.md"], "commit_message_suggestion": "feat: Profile Manager foundation (Epic 1 Tasks 1.1-1.3)\n\n- Pydantic models with full validation (conport required, name format, time windows)\n- YAML parser with discovery and batch loading\n- Detection engine with weighted scoring (5 signals, ADHD thresholds)\n- Config generator transforms profiles to Claude config.json\n- 4 default profile templates (developer, researcher, architect, minimal)\n- UI design research synthesis document (13.5K words, 4-phase roadmap)\n\nAll tests passing, ready for CLI implementation (Task 1.4)", "session_duration_hours": 1.5, "resume_ready": true, "epic_1_completion_date": "2025-10-15", "git_commits": ["6190f85 - Epic 1 Task 1.4 CLI commands", "da01cfd - Epic 1 Tasks 1.1-1.3 foundation"], "lines_added_epic_1": "1,780+ lines (models, parser, detector, config generator, CLI)", "next_focus": "UI Phase 1: Event Bus + ADHD Theme System", "git_latest": "7c76391 - Merge with Claude Code Router + LiteLLM", "phase_1_week_1_goal": "Event bus operational, themes switchable, libtmux foundation", "architecture_analysis_complete": true, "deep_dives_total": 7, "decisions_logged": [37, 38, 39], "synthesis_updated": "docs/ARCHITECTURE-CONSOLIDATION-SYNTHESIS.md enhanced with Decisions #31-32", "total_container_savings": "-42% (19\u219211 containers)", "session_complete": true, "git_commits_this